full_text: Prince Joachim of Belgium, Archduke of Austria-Este , Prince Imperial of Austria, Prince Royal of Hungary and Bohemia, Prince of Modena, is the younger son and third child of Lorenz, Archduke of Austria-Este and Princess Astrid of Belgium.
title: Prince Joachim, Archduke of Austria-Este
